high_descs: Go to the other side of the table in front of you.
Pick up the gold plate from the table.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the gold plate inside and chill it, then take it out.
Turn around to face the table.
Put the gold plate on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled gold plate on the table.

high_descs: Move around the left side of the table, to the other side of the table, turn right to face the tan plate on the table.
Pick up the plate on the table.
Bring the plate to the fridge behind you.
Chill the plate in the fridge.
Take the chilled plate back to the table behind you.
Put the chilled plate on the right side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled plate on the table.

high_descs: Make a right around the kitchen island.
Pick up the gold plate from the kitchen island countertop.
Turn around to walk towards the fridge.
Chill the gold plate in the fridge, removing it afterwards.
Turn around to walk back to the kitchen island.
Set the gold plate back on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Chill a gold plate to put on the kitchen island countertop.
